title: Be Comfortable Not Knowing | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Be Comfortable Not Knowing | Joel Osteen
description:
Sometimes God asks us to step out in faith when we don’t understand. If you’ll make the choice to trust Him, you’ll see Him show out in your life.

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
